<h4>Utility Classes 
</h4>

<p>Bootstrap provides utility classes, which is essential to style your labels according to the condition</p>
<ul>
    <li>Muted : Disabled Text
    </li>
    <li>Warning : Warning text to indicating caution 

    </li>
